## Spodoptera frugiperda (Fall Armyworm) - Demo GFF3 Annotation File

### Download Real GFF3 Files from NCBI:

**Option 1: Fall Armyworm (Spodoptera frugiperda)**
- **NCBI Genome:** https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/12974
- **Direct GFF3 Download:** https://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genomes/all/GCF/021/871/675/GCF_021871675.1_ASM2187167v1/GCF_021871675.1_ASM2187167v1_genomic.gff.gz
- **Size:** ~50 MB (compressed)
- **Genes:** ~18,000 protein-coding genes

**Option 2: Alternative Assembly (iPREB_ACEmbly)**
- **NCBI Accession:** GCA_904972905.1
- **Download:** https://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genomes/all/GCA/904/972/905/GCA_904972905.1/GCA_904972905.1_iPREB_ACEmbly_v1.0/GCA_904972905.1_iPREB_ACEmbly_v1.0_genomic.gff.gz

